title: Fingerprint sensor is not working properly
content:
After having issues unlocking with a fingerprint and trying obvious solutions like cleaning the sensor and my fingers, I deleted the existing fingerprint  to add a new entry. 

But I couldn't finish the process because it fails to register my fingerprint most of the time and the process gets cancelled.

I think this might be a hardware issue as the fingerprint was not working optimally from the start and now it's not usable at all.

Any help would be appreciated.

Thanks,
Temesgen
